description:
&lt;p&gt;NHS Stockport CCG are looking to recruit an experienced and dynamic leader to head up the CHC Team. This role will support the delivery of the national framework for NHS Continuing Health Care which is both a national and local priority area. Providing professional nursing leadership, line management and technical expertise to the CHC team to enable maintenance and development of the CHC work programme will be the key focus of the role. The successful candidate will have had significant experience and knowledge of the Continuing Healthcare Framework, and will work closely with the Executive Nurse and the wider nursing and quality team to support the CCG&#39;s objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focus purely on the delivery of the CHC framework and the management of the CHC team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the newly appointed care home lead to enable support to care homes will continue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameAnita RolfeJob titleExecutive NurseEmail addressanitarolfe@nhs.netTelephone number07775004702Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Via her PA: Alison Newton (alison.newton3@nhs.net), 07775004702&lt;/p&gt;
